data.description: Presenting 30131 Candleberry Drive, an impeccably maintained, breathtaking, coastal style villa nestled on a picturesque pond within the highly coveted Jack Nicklaus premier golf course amenity rich community, Bayside. This residence exudes refinement at every turn, showcasing exquisite craftsmanship and unparalleled features. Step through the welcoming foyer adorned with elegant luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout main living areas, intricate crown molding details, and a tranquil ambiance that permeates the entire open-concept layout. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary haven, boasting a sprawling center island, gleaming granite countertops, gas cooktop, vent hood, wall-mounted microwave and oven, and a convenient pantry. Flowing seamlessly from the kitchen, the charming dining area offers an ideal setting for gatherings. Enhanced by an exquisite corner fireplace, the great room exudes an air of sophistication, perfect for effortless conversation, and grants access to the expansive patio overlooking the tranquil pond. Retreat to the luxurious primary suite on the main level, featuring a deep-tray ceiling, a refined sitting area with panoramic pond vistas, a generous walk-in closet, and a lavish ensuite complete with separate vanities and a tiled glass stall shower. Step out onto the paver patio to bask in the coastal breeze and savor the breathtaking pond views. A full-sized laundry room and mudroom area with built-in cabinetry lead to the finished two-car garage, boasting an epoxy floor and custom storage solutions. Upstairs, a spacious family room awaits, accompanied by an extensive storage room. Three additional bedrooms on the upper level offer individualized features, with two sharing a well-appointed hall bath boasting a double sink vanity. The third bedroom enjoys private access to another beautifully appointed hall bath. Experience resort-style living at its finest in the esteemed Bayside Community, renowned for its award-winning design and an array of amenities including a Jack Nicklaus Signature Golf Course, 2 restaurants with bars, lawn care, snow removal, pools with food and beverage, trails, a dog park, community beach, fitness center, recreational activities, tennis courts, pickle-ball courts, playground, beach shuttle, and more—all conveniently covered by the HOA and a one-time sports fee. Welcome home to unparalleled luxury and leisure.
